# This directory contains a partial copy of the Cloudflare Terraform provider v5.
# We track go.mod, go.sum, internal/, and shim/ — the minimum needed for Go to
# resolve the replace directive and for the shim to import internal.NewProvider().
#
# To update: bump TERRAFORM_PROVIDER_VERSION in Makefile, run `make provider-shim`,
# then commit the changes to this directory.
#
# Ignore everything except what Go needs
*
!.gitignore
!go.mod
!go.sum
!internal/
!internal/**
!shim/
!shim/**
